    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously won't believe how gorgeous this car is. It\u2019s been babied since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a scratch anywhere, the interior is absolutely spotless, and it drives like a total dream. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it just as much as I have. Come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered legend. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features a documented dual-VANOS overhaul and preventative rod bearing replacement, ensuring the valvetrain remains within factory tolerances. Power is transmitted through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally flawless, featuring reinforced subframe mounting points and a suspension geometry utilizing OEM Sachs dampers and fresh bushings for telepathic handling. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the Nappa leather interior remains supple with no bolster wear. This is a concours-ready specimen with a fully synchronized service history, offering the tactile feedback and linear power delivery that defined the golden era of M-division engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Original paint. No mechanical issues. Spotless interior. Service records available. Clean title.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional 2021 BMW M2 Competition in Hockenheim Silver Metallic. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, and free of any swirls, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the black Dakota leather with blue stitching remains taut and pristine, still retaining that new-car aroma. Every surface, from the carbon fiber inserts to the Alcantara-wrapped M-sport steering wheel, shows zero signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having followed a rigorous break-in procedure and receiving scheduled maintenance exclusively at authorized BMW centers. With low miles and a documented history, this is a rare opportunity to own a modern classic that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Included are both keys, all original manuals, and a comprehensive service file.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
