      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in showroom condition. This specimen represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring an impeccable exterior finish paired with a pristine, meticulously preserved interior. Every mechanical system has been rigorously vetted to ensure it meets our exacting standards for performance and reliability. For the discerning individual who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle offers an unparalleled ownership experience and remains a definitive example of automotive excellence.",
