      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m so excited for whoever gets to take this beauty home. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and there isn't a single flaw to be found. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next adventure. You\u2019ve gotta come see it in person to believe how perfect it is!",
