    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Alpine White. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative: the rod bearings have been replaced with VAC coated units, the double VANOS system has been completely overhauled with Beisan components, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced. The chassis retains its factory rigidity, supported by an uncompromised suspension geometry and a 3.64 limited-slip differential. The exterior finish remains in showroom state with zero evidence of oxidation or clear coat failure. A purist\u2019s specimen with documented service history and zero mechanical deficiencies.",
